請大家保持安全距離<br />\n3) 相信警方當日會投放大量警力於各區&ldquo;維持秩序&ldquo;，大家小心<br />\n4) 是次目的為記念無法團圓的家庭，不建議有暴力場面，亦盡量避免衝突發生<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各參加者帶備蠟燭到場🕯<br />\n<br />\n入黎telegram以獲得最新資訊<br />\nTG Channel Link:<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/SilentCandleNight\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSilentCandleNight&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=12e69eee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/SilentCandleNight</a><br />\n<br />\n#平安夜 #Dec24 #記念活動 #Save12HKyouths #毋忘義士 #釋放十二 #武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9E9wr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9E9wr7.jpg&h=9bc16342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FnryFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FnryFt.jpg&h=6e2e0b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCBoATP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCBoATP.jpg&h=7935e4d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動缺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推post同分享出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4702225fc9a12fc1c40169a64c6a2fa217677b07","tid":2336042,"uid":337279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a94545e79954d39d505c77d7112ede06fb62381","tid":2336042,"uid":337279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=